sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
        participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI)
        participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
        participant MR as model-registry<br/>(proxy)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP

        Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTPS, Platform Auth
        IstioGW->>MR: Forward request<br/>HTTP, Istio mTLS
        MR->>DB: INSERT registered_model<br/>DB protocol, Optional TLS<br/>Auth: Username/password
        DB-->>MR: Model record
        MR-->>IstioGW: 201 Created (JSON)
        IstioGW-->>Client: Response
    end

    %% Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over KServe,MR: Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
        participant KServe as KServe
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Controller as controller-manager<br/>8081/TCP Health<br/>8443/TCP Metrics

        KServe->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>HTTPS, TLS, ServiceAccount
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event (ISVC created)<br/>HTTPS, TLS, ServiceAccount
        Controller->>MR: POST /api/.../inference_services<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        MR->>DB: INSERT inference_service
        DB-->>MR: Record created
        MR-->>Controller: 201 Created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH ISVC (add labels + finalizer)<br/>HTTPS, TLS, ServiceAccount
    end

    %% Flow 3: Model Download via CSI
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over KServeInit,ModelStore: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
        participant KServeInit as KServe Init Container<br/>(storage-initializer)
        participant ModelStore as Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/OCI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        KServeInit->>MR: GET model-registry://model/version<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP, No Auth
        MR->>DB: SELECT model_artifact<br/>DB protocol
        DB-->>MR: Artifact URI (s3://bucket/model)
        MR-->>KServeInit: Resolved storage URI
        KServeInit->>ModelStore: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
        ModelStore-->>KServeInit: Model files
    end

    %% Flow 4: Async Model Upload
    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over AsyncJob,OCIReg: Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job
        participant AsyncJob as async-upload-job<br/>(Python)
        participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant OCIReg as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        AsyncJob->>S3: Download model files<br/>HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
        S3-->>AsyncJob: Model artifacts
        AsyncJob->>OCIReg: Push model as OCI artifact<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
        OCIReg-->>AsyncJob: Push confirmation
        AsyncJob->>MR: POST /api/.../model_artifacts<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        MR-->>AsyncJob: Artifact registered
    end

    %% Flow 5: UI Model Browsing
    rect rgb(255, 249, 230)
        Note over Browser,Catalog: Flow 5: UI Model Browsing
        participant Browser as Browser
        participant BFF as UI BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant Catalog as model-catalog-server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

        Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/model_registry/{name}/registered_models<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, User token
        BFF->>MR: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP, Forwarded token
        MR-->>BFF: Model list (JSON)
        BFF-->>Browser: Proxied response

        Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/catalog/models<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, User token
        BFF->>Catalog: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/catalog_models<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP, Forwarded token
        Catalog-->>BFF: Catalog models (JSON)
        BFF-->>Browser: Proxied response

        Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/namespaces<br/>User token
        BFF->>K8sAPI: List namespaces<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, User token
        K8sAPI-->>BFF: Namespace list
        BFF-->>Browser: Accessible namespaces
    end
